wget patched to make --no-verbose option outputs a progress bar.

It will look like this:

    $ wget -nv ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/wget/wget-1.12.tar.bz2
    38% [=============>      ]      614,880 79.5K/s eta 13s

You can add the --no-verbose option into wgetrc file:

    # Verbose mode: tons of information.
    # Command-line equivalent: -v or --verbose, or -nv or --no-verbose
    verbose = off

NOTE: This version conflicts with wget.
